{
  "stem": "27507.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was something that was, of course, in the end, I think, my aunts and so on, they didn't want to bring anything almost to hide it and so on because one was also afraid of that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But those people were literally dying of hunger and were-- were trying to snatch to get something to eat even though-- you know, even if it meant that they had to suffer a beating and being beaten or screamed at.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And of course, not-- again, there were those terrible contrasts everywhere because at the same time there was-- at the same time that there was the horrible poverty and hunger, there were as well people who ate very well.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were restaurants, and there were cafes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were cafes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was even-- there was cultural life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think he's finishing now, no?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was cultural life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were theaters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were academies.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were-- academies, I mean, there-- that's a Polish word again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's something like certain official festivities, some ceremonies, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there were theaters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were different kinds of theaters, although I wasn't to a theater myself, but I know that-- well I walked to one theater that I will mention to-- [NON-ENGLISH] theater.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there were theaters were on bigger and smaller scale.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there were as well restaurants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were as well-- there were as well coffee-- coffee houses, certainly places to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, in fact, there were places to eat and eat very well in ghetto, practically till the almost very end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were still at the very end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then, there were many restaurants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at the same time that people ate in the restaurant, there were people sitting next the restaurant and starving and-- and begging.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
